<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About</title>
    <!-- google font link  -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;700&family=Forum&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <!-- css link -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./style/style.css" />

    <!-- 
    - favicon
  -->
    <link
      rel="shortcut icon"
      href="./assest/img/second-cup.png"
      type="image/png"
    />

    <style>
      body {
        overflow-y: auto; /* Ensure vertical scrolling is enabled */
      }

      .main {
        margin-top: 190px;
      }

      .about-us-section {
        background-color: #f8f8f8; /* Light background color */
        padding: 50px; /* Spacing inside the section */
        margin: 30px auto; /* Center the section */
        max-width: 900px; /* Max width of the section */
        border-radius: 10px; /* Rounded corners */
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Subtle shadow */
      }

      .about-us-section h1 {
        color: #000000; /* Dark heading color */
        font-size: 36px; /* Large font size for title */
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .about-us-section p {
        color: #555; /* Grey text color */
        font-size: 18px; /* Comfortable reading size */
        line-height: 1.6; /* Line height for readability */
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .about-us-section h2 {
        color: #000000; /* Darker heading for section title */
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-top: 40px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .about-us-section ul {
        list-style-type: none; /* Remove default bullet points */
        padding: 0;
      }

      .about-us-section ul li {
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #555;
        padding: 5px 0; /* Space between each item */
        margin-left: 20px; /* Indent the list */
        position: relative;
      }

      .about-us-section ul li:before {
        content: "•"; /* Custom bullet point */
        color: #f39c12; /* Accent color */
        font-size: 20px;
        position: absolute;
        left: -20px;
      }

      .about-us-section strong {
        color: #e67e22; /* Highlight key text */
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('nav') %>

    <main class="main">
      <div class="about-us-section">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>
          Welcome to <strong>Second Cup</strong>, a place where coffee meets
          community! Nestled in the heart of Besisahar-7 Lamjung, our cafe is
          more than just a spot to grab your favorite brew — it’s an experience.
          Whether you're here for a cozy chat over cappuccinos or seeking the
          perfect espresso on the go, our expertly crafted beverages and warm
          ambiance are sure to make you feel right at home.
        </p>

        <p>
          At <strong>Second Cup</strong>, we believe in the artistry of coffee.
          That’s why we also offer our renowned <strong>Barista School</strong>,
          where aspiring coffee enthusiasts can learn the craft of brewing the
          perfect cup. From understanding coffee beans to mastering the espresso
          machine, our experienced instructors provide hands-on training in a
          relaxed, friendly environment.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Quality:</strong> Every cup of coffee is made with the
            highest-quality beans, handpicked to ensure a superior taste.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Community:</strong> We strive to create a space where people
            from all walks of life can gather, relax, and enjoy great
            conversation.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Education:</strong> Through our barista school, we aim to
            spread knowledge and passion for coffee, nurturing the next
            generation of coffee artisans.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          Whether you're a casual coffee lover or an aspiring barista,
          <strong>Second Cup</strong> is the place for you. Come by and let us
          share our passion for coffee with you!
        </p>
      </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('footer') %>
    <script src="./style/main.js"></script>
    <script
      type="module"
      src="https://unpkg.com/ionicons@5.5.2/dist/ionicons/ionicons.esm.js"
    ></script>
    <script
      nomodule
      src="https://unpkg.com/ionicons@5.5.2/dist/ionicons/ionicons.js"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
